videos.description: Kansas' Malik Newman sets up Udoka Azubuike down low for the loud dunk to open the game.
videos.headline: Azubuike emphatically throws down opening dunk

videos.description: Kansas' Lagerald Vick lobs a pass up to Udoka Azubuike for the alley-oop slam in the first half.
videos.headline: Vick sets up Azubuike on the oop

videos.description: Kansas' Devonte' Graham lobs a pass up to Lagerald Vick for the alley-oop finish.
videos.headline: Graham connects with Vick for the alley-oop

videos.description: Kansas' Sviatoslav Mykhailiuk splits the defense and throws down the emphatic dunk in the first half.
videos.headline: Mykhailiuk soars for the one-handed slam

videos.description: Kansas' Devonte' Graham lofts a pass up to Udoka Azubuike for the alley-oop finish.
videos.headline: Graham finds Azubuike for the alley-oop

videos.description: Stanford's Robert Cartwright lobs a pass at the rim to Michael Humphrey for the alley-oop slam in the first half.
videos.headline: Cartwright dishes to Humphrey for the alley-oop

videos.description: Kansas' Sviatoslav Mykhailiuk dishes the ball down low to Udoka Azubuike for the emphatic jam in the second half.
videos.headline: Azubuike throws down loud two-handed slam

videos.description: Kansas' Sviatoslav Mykhailiuk splits through the defense and finishes the left-handed layup in the second half.
videos.headline: Mykhailiuk converts lefty layup

videos.description: Stanford's Kezie Okpala tries taking it down the lane but is rejected by Kansas' Mitch Lightfoot.
videos.headline: Lightfoot executes chase-down block

videos.description: Kansas' Lagerald Vick knocks down the contested mid-range jumper for the chance at a 3-point play.
videos.headline: Vick sinks layup for and-1 chance

videos.description: Kansas' Udoka Azubuike hauls in the offensive rebound and slams home the dunk for a chance at a 3-point play.
videos.headline: Azubuike's converts putback slam
